reviewText: Love it, replacing a damaged one that my husband loves so much
I saw this on TV a few years ago and have been looking for it ever since.  Just as good as I remember.

This CD, and as well as the others from Banco Popular, offer an excellent collection of typical Puerto Rican music.  We got them recently and it is the perfect music for upbeat holiday parties. Excellent disc!

Claro que soy un Puerto Riqueo pero vivo en Michigan asi que es un alivio recibir un buen CD de musica boricua.
